    { question: "What exactly is AI Google Business Profile optimization for builders?", answer: "It\'s a system that uses artificial intelligence to manage your Google Business Profile and attract more building project enquiries from local searches. Building is one of the most competitive trades on Google — homeowners planning extensions, loft conversions, or renovations invest significant time comparing builders online before making contact. AI optimization ensures your profile stands out. The AI handles three things: first, it configures your profile with the correct categories, service listings, and descriptions targeting high-value building searches. Second, it automatically sends review requests to your clients at the optimal time after project completion — for builders, this is typically a few days after handover when the client has settled into the finished space. Third, the AI responds to every review professionally, creating a public portfolio of satisfied clients. The result is a profile that communicates quality, reliability, and professionalism — the three things homeowners prioritise when choosing a builder for a major project." },
